system websites, none of them are

00:32:08.860 --> 00:32:12.310
as much fun to use as WordPress.

00:32:12.310 --> 00:32:16.610
If you notice there I said fun
because I don't like to have to think

00:32:16.610 --> 00:32:20.290
about what I need to do next
in order to update my website

00:32:20.290 --> 00:32:22.700
or create a new blog
post or upload a video.

00:32:22.700 --> 00:32:27.230
I would like to be able to go
step, step, step without having

00:32:27.230 --> 00:32:28.400
to think about it at all.

00:32:30.360 --> 00:32:32.440
I just want you to think about it.

