thing that happens to me is

00:36:33.610 --> 00:36:38.250
when I go to a website to fill
out a lot of form and the forms

00:36:38.250 --> 00:36:42.780
either aren't labeled or
the label is off to the side

00:36:42.780 --> 00:36:44.770
and it isn't connected
to the field.

00:36:45.810 --> 00:36:48.570
Just to explain this for
somebody who isn't really sure

00:36:48.570 --> 00:36:49.750
what I'm talking about here.

00:36:49.750 --> 00:36:52.500
When you use the screen
reader, your general ways

00:36:52.500 --> 00:36:56.360
of navigating the screen
are tab and shift-tab.

00:36:56.360 --> 00:37:00.190
In a perfect world,
a form would announce the field

00:37:00.190 --> 00:37:05.270
along with any instructions for
that field as you come to it.

00:37:05.270 --> 00:37:09.420
If I press tab and the first field
wants my first name it should say,

00:37:09.420 --> 00:37:12.290
first name but quite
often it doesn't.

00:37:12.290 --> 00:37:15.760
It'll just say edit or blank
or empty or something along

00:37:15.760 --> 00:37:18.580
and I will have to use my
arrow keys and go word by word

00:37:18.580 --> 00:37:23.430
or line by line to find where I
need to put the information in.

00:37:24.710 --> 00:37:28.190
If you're using a form be
sure to test your form.

00:37:28.190 --> 00:37:32.050
Have somebody who uses a screen
reader, test it for you make sure

00:37:32.050 --> 00:37:33.590
that it's not just accessible.

00:37:33.590 --> 00:37:36.050
As I said earlier there could
be things that are accessible

00:37:36.050 --> 00:37:40.230
that are not workable that
have poor workflow designs.

00:37:40.230 --> 00:37:44.370
If you're using a form habit tested
send it to somebody and ask them

00:37:44.370 --> 00:37:45.780
if they'll fill it in
for you and tell them

00:37:45.780 --> 00:37:47.960
if they do you'll give them a
social media shoutout or something

00:37:47.960 --> 00:37:49.300
to make it worth their while.

00:37:50.669 --> 00:37:52.190
>> DANIELLE: A
little discount code.

00:37:52.190 --> 00:37:53.050
>> MAXWELL: There you go.

00:37:53.050 --> 00:37:55.340
A discount code exactly.

00:37:56.590 --> 00:37:58.390
Beyond that just to
finish off the thought

00:37:58.390 --> 00:38:01.660
about forms the other thing
that just really ticks me off

00:38:01.660 --> 00:38:04.690
and I don't get mad
about much is if I manage

00:38:04.690 --> 00:38:07.360
to make my way to the
end of the form, and then

00:38:07.360 --> 00:38:11.130
for some reason the way they
