of knowing that it's in play

00:41:04.310 --> 00:41:08.820
and a way to know when was
the last time it updated

00:41:08.820 --> 00:41:12.420
because quite often with
those Save As You Go things,

00:41:12.420 --> 00:41:15.109
they don't report to the
notifications settings

00:41:15.109 --> 00:41:17.909
on my screen reader to tell me
that something just popped up

00:41:17.909 --> 00:41:19.460
on the screen.

00:41:19.460 --> 00:41:25.270
Knowing that it's being saved or
having the last saved time marker

00:41:25.270 --> 00:41:28.990
that most of them use next to
the submit button would be,

00:41:28.990 --> 00:41:30.140
are very helpful things.

00:41:30.140 --> 00:41:32.910
