know if it's being saved or not

00:41:32.910 --> 00:41:36.610
and then be able to find the place
on the screen where I can see

00:41:36.610 --> 00:41:38.330
how long ago did it save it.

00:41:39.610 --> 00:41:42.220
Another thing that's really
good, and this is, in addition,

00:41:42.220 --> 00:41:45.400
to Save As You Go
is-- I can't tell you

00:41:45.400 --> 00:41:49.670
how many times I fill out a form
and I don't get an error message

00:41:49.670 --> 00:41:54.240
and I press submit, everything
goes, but it never tells me

00:41:54.240 --> 00:41:55.380
that I was successful.

00:41:55.380 --> 00:41:56.670
It doesn't say thank you.

00:41:56.670 --> 00:41:58.770
It doesn't say your
submission was received.

00:41:58.770 --> 00:41:59.940
It doesn't say, nothing.

00:42:01.360 --> 00:42:04.680
Sometimes I can go to the URL
and at the end of the URL,

00:42:04.680 --> 00:42:07.490
you can see where
the URL has changed

00:42:07.490 --> 00:42:11.800
because your submission went through
but most of the time you can't.

00:42:11.800 --> 00:42:16.320
If they don't send you a
confirmation email, because a lot

00:42:16.320 --> 00:42:19.840
of them don't automatically do
that, and a lot of them don't have

00:42:19.840 --> 00:42:24.750
that check box to select,
to have a copy set to yourself.

00:42:24.750 --> 00:42:28.430
If you don't know that it's done
you have two choices, you can

00:42:28.430 --> 00:42:30.510
either sit there and wait.

00:42:30.510 --> 00:42:33.150
You can try entering
the information again.

00:42:33.150 --> 00:42:35.310
You can get mad and leave.

00:42:35.310 --> 00:42:38.820
There really aren't good
outcomes for the other person

00:42:38.820 --> 00:42:41.890
if I don't know what I'm
doing based on the information

00:42:41.890 --> 00:42:44.870
that I can find on the screen and
of course, with a screen reader

00:42:44.870 --> 00:42:48.399
that is text characters,
that is images

00:42:48.399 --> 00:42:50.200
that have been assigned alt text,

00:42:50.200 --> 00:42:54.200
those are buttons that have been
assigned alt text, those are links

00:42:54.200 --> 00:42:58.290
that have been actually given
names instead of an unnamed link.

